---
import PageLayout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
const metadata = {
  title: 'Mission',
  description:
    'My mission, workflow, and the full stack web marketing services I offer: from strategy and branding to web development, e-commerce, and ongoing optimization.',
  robots: {
    index: false,
    follow: false,
  },
};
---

<PageLayout metadata={metadata}>
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-12 px-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-6 text-center">Full Stack Web Marketing</h1>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6 text-center">Your Project Realized from A to Z!</h2>

    <p class="mb-10 text-lg text-center">
      Over the years, I have acquired a broad set of cross-functional skills that allow me to cover multiple roles and
      support the different teams throughout the entire project lifecycle. From developing an idea, implementing it on
      the web, promoting it, and analyzing the results ‚Äî every step is essential to achieving success together!
    </p>

    <!-- Ideation & Strategy -->
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4 mt-10">
      <span class="text-2xl">üí°</span>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Ideation & Strategy</h2>
    </div>
    <p class="mb-2">Every successful project starts with a strong plan:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-8 mb-6 space-y-1">
      <li>Market research and competitor analysis</li>
      <li>Defining customer personas and user journeys</li>
      <li>Brainstorming sessions to shape product/service ideas</li>
      <li>Vision and mission development</li>
      <li>SMART goals and KPI definition</li>
      <li>Communication plan: channels, tone of voice, content frequency</li>
      <li>Project management: task planning, timelines, milestones</li>
    </ul>

    <!-- Branding & Visual Communication -->
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4 mt-10">
      <span class="text-2xl">üé®</span>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Branding & Visual Communication</h2>
    </div>
    <p class="mb-2">Creating a consistent and memorable brand identity:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-8 mb-6 space-y-1">
      <li>
        Digital and print marketing materials: Logo, business cards, letterheads, banners, brochures, flyers, roll-ups
        and custom graphics
      </li>
      <li>Photography: products, locations, team</li>
      <li>Videos, reels, animated content</li>
      <li>Copywriting for websites, brochures, blogs, social media</li>
      <li>Packaging design</li>
      <li>Tone of voice guidelines and graphic brand style guide</li>
    </ul>

    <!-- Web Development & E-commerce -->
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4 mt-10">
      <span class="text-2xl">üåê</span>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Web Development & E-commerce</h2>
    </div>
    <p class="mb-2">Building scalable, high-performing digital platforms:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-8 mb-6 space-y-1">
      <li>Informational website: responsive, SEO optimized</li>
      <li>E-commerce website: product population with images, descriptions, categories</li>
      <li>ERP selection and integration with the CMS for order management and invoicing</li>
      <li>Full stack development: Next.js, React, Astro, Tailwind CSS</li>
      <li>Database and authentication: Supabase (DB + auth)</li>
      <li>Quality control: linting, Husky, GitHub Actions, Vercel deployment</li>
      <li>Advanced features: product filters, wishlist, reviews, website internal search engine marketing</li>
      <li>Ticket System, AI ChatBot integration</li>
      <li>CMS or Headless CMS for flexible content management</li>
      <li>Security & GDPR compliance</li>
      <li>Mobile performance optimization & Core Web Vitals</li>
      <li>Technical maintenance: bug fixes, security updates, performance monitoring</li>
    </ul>

    <!-- Digital Marketing & Promotion -->
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4 mt-10">
      <span class="text-2xl">üìà</span>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Digital Marketing & Promotion</h2>
    </div>
    <p class="mb-2">Driving traffic, engagement, and conversions:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-8 mb-6 space-y-1">
      <li>Social media marketing & content scheduling with Hootsuite</li>
      <li>Email marketing and automation (Mailchimp/Mailup, drip campaigns)</li>
      <li>Blog integration for inbound marketing</li>
      <li>Paid advertising campaigns: Google Ads, Meta Ads, LinkedIn Ads</li>
      <li>Remarketing and retargeting strategies</li>
      <li>Lead generation and dedicated landing pages</li>
      <li>SEO best practices and local SEO</li>
      <li>Advanced SEO: link building, pillar content, schema markup</li>
    </ul>

    <!-- Community & Engagement -->
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4 mt-10">
      <span class="text-2xl">ü§ù</span>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Community & Engagement</h2>
    </div>
    <p class="mb-2">Building relationships and maintaining trust:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-8 mb-6 space-y-1">
      <li>Customer service management on social channels</li>
      <li>Online community or forum creation (if relevant)</li>
      <li>Event management: webinars, online events, appointment calendar with Calendly</li>
      <li>Reputation management: monitoring reviews and feedback</li>
      <li>Loyalty programs, upsell and cross-sell strategies on the product pages</li>
    </ul>

    <!-- Analysis & Optimization -->
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4 mt-10">
      <span class="text-2xl">üìä</span>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Analysis, Optimization & Growth</h2>
    </div>
    <p class="mb-2">Continuous improvement to maximize ROI ensuring long-term success and scalability:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-8 mb-6 space-y-1">
      <li>Monitoring KPIs and campaign performance</li>
      <li>Google Analytics, GA4, Tag Manager, heatmaps</li>
      <li>Conversion rate optimization (CRO)</li>
      <li>A/B testing on landing pages, emails, ads</li>
      <li>Regular reporting: insights, recommendations, and strategy adjustments</li>
    </ul>
  </main>
</PageLayout>
